  'line_118' => 'To request a refund due to payment issues, please contact our customer support team as soon as possible. Provide details about the payment problem and any relevant information to expedite the refund process. Once your refund request is approved, we will initiate the refund process according to our refund policy and European Union regulations. Refunds will be issued to the original payment method within a reasonable timeframe.',
